The '''Turan''' were a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] species with orange skin.

Some Turans pursued careers in music, like the popular band who played in the main hall of a [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] [[Casino/Legends|casino]] around [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]]. [[Base nose flute]]s, [[electric harp]]s and [[soft percussion drum]]s gave their music an "insistent, exhilarating tune" that stirred the bounty hunter [[Dengar/Legends|Dengar]] deeply.

